lead_paragraph: Paris St Germain's league record 36-game unbeaten streak came to an abrupt halt when they lost 2-1 at Olympique Lyonnais on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: PSG's 36-Game Unbeaten Streak Shattered at Lyon
